trans-unit.source: Provides an editing user interface (UI) for a data control field.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en redigering brukergrensesnittet (UI) for et datafelt for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This editor is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> controls.
trans-unit.target: Dette redigeringsprogrammet er brukt internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataControlFieldTypeEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataControlFieldTypeEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Edits the specified value, using the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> and <xref:System.IServiceProvider> objects.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer den angitte verdien, ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> og <xref:System.IServiceProvider>objekter.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that indicates the context of the object being edited.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som angir konteksten for objektet som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IServiceProvider> containing a reference to the associated designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IServiceProvider>som inneholder en referanse til den tilknyttede utformeren.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The final value of the object after it has been edited.
trans-unit.target: Den endelige verdien til objektet etter at den er redigert.

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style associated with this editor, using the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering stilen knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet, ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that indicates the context of the object being edited.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som angir konteksten for objektet som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> value representing the editing style of this editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref> verdien som representerer redigering stilen for dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_Modal" name="Modal" href=""></xref>.
